sequenceDiagram
actor Kasztelan
participant Browser
participant View as OrdersView
participant SSUJ as SSUJService
participant Parser as DataParser
participant DB as Database

%% =========================
%% OPEN ORDERS PANEL
%% =========================
Kasztelan ->> Browser: Open "Zarządzenia SSUJ"
Browser ->> View: GET /ssuj/orders/

%% =========================
%% FETCH FROM EXTERNAL SOURCE
%% =========================
View ->> SSUJ: getLatestOrders()

SSUJ ->> SSUJ: call external SSUJ website/API
SSUJ -->> View: raw HTML / JSON / documents

%% =========================
%% PARSING
%% =========================
View ->> Parser: parse(raw_data)
Parser ->> Parser: extract orders, dates, titles
Parser -->> View: structured orders list

%% =========================
%% OPTIONAL CACHE
%% =========================
View ->> DB: store latest SSUJ snapshot
DB -->> View: saved

%% =========================
%% RENDER
%% =========================
View -->> Browser: render orders list
Browser -->> Kasztelan: display SSUJ orders
